title: Social Studies Test 1
intro_text:
Social Studies

Welcome to the GED® Social Studies Practice Test!

This test is 24 questions, which is about half the length of an official GED® Test. You will not be timed.

The goal is to give you practice on the types of questions you will see on the GED® test and to give you a study plan for what you need to brush up on for the test.

If you are unsure of an answer, click “Review Question Later” to come back to the question later.
